    ],
    "originating_user_signal": "Director 2026-05-24: 'I have a git organization called oagp-org... move this repo... and same for orgdef-spec/orgdef'. Sharpened by Director shortly after: 'catdef is truly different. It's just a data spec. roledef, orgdef, memodef are all part of OAGP. Transcripts are a subcategory of memos.'",
